tafsir[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,"Mbela A anndii oon fennoowo njoɓdi ñande darnga."
  107,2,"Oon woni duñiroowo alyatiime e mbaadi cattundi."
  107,3,"O reerɗatah e ñamminde miskiin o reerɗinirtah goɗɗo ñamminde miskiin."
  107,4,"Halkude e leptude ɓeen welsandiiɓe nder juulde mum en, ɓe ngoƴaako nde haa waktu hende yawta."
  107,5,"107:4"
  107,6,"ɓeen waɗooɓe yiingo e golle mum en e juulde mum en, ɓe cellintah golle ngam Alla."
  107,7,"Hoɓe kaɗa wallude tanaa mum en ko lorla alah e wallirde ɓe ɗuum."
